import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { FormBuilder, FormGroup, Validators } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-add-camera', templateUrl: './add-camera.component.html', styleUrls: ['./add-camera.component.css'], }) export class AddCameraComponent { faceCameraForm: FormGroup; activeTab: string = 'faceCamera'; constructor(private fb: FormBuilder) { this.faceCameraForm = this.fb.group({ cameratype: ['face_cam', Validators.required], // Default value "face_cam" connectionType: ['usb', Validators.required], // Default option "USB" usbInput: [''], // USB input field (shown conditionally) urlInput: [''], // URL input field (shown conditionally) }); } ngOnInit() {} setActiveTab(tab: string) { this.activeTab = tab; } onSave() { if (this.faceCameraForm.valid) { const formData = this.faceCameraForm.value; console.log('Form Data:', formData); alert('Form Saved Successfully!'); // Add API call to save data } else { alert('Please fill out the form correctly.'); } } }
